Enter ""odd"", ""even"", or ""neither"".",\text{even},\text{even},True,True,parser,,"To determine whether the function \( f(f(g(f(g(f(x)))))) \) is even, odd, or neither, we need to analyze the properties of the functions \( f \) and \( g \) and how they interact under composition.

